    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Level 2 against a required Level 3 due to single-condition testing; this gap is accepted given the prescriptive nature of ASTM F1717 and the low variability observed across N=11 constructs and two laboratories. E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs; maximum QoI difference 6.3%, within the <10% bound. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for Medium assurance level at Model Risk Level 3.",
